DISCLAIMER:

This is a MOCK API server created for development and testing purposes.
It is based on the unofficial reverse-engineered NUS NextBus API specification.

This software is NOT affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to:
- National University of Singapore (NUS)
- ComfortDelGro Corporation
- Any official NUS NextBus service

The mock data, bus routes, schedules, and other information provided by this
API are for DEMONSTRATION and DEVELOPMENT purposes only and should not be used
for actual navigation or transportation planning.

For official NUS shuttle bus information, please refer to:
https://uci.nus.edu.sg/oca/mobilityservices/getting-around-nus/

The original API specification was documented by Hu Jialun.
Source: https://github.com/SuibianP/nus-nextbus-new-api
